{"tid":1812903,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"O記狗賊旺角執勤遺失裝備","createTime":"2020-01-06T00:45:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-06T01:02:24.000Z","uid":51271,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"284d7c0f409a725cea7fd9f3385f4cce70901b35","tid":1812903,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T00:45:55.000Z","msg":"4名有組織罪案及三合會調查科（Ｏ記）探員，昨日（4日）早上在旺角執勤時，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>意外遺失兩支電筒、一副護目鏡及一部平板電腦。</strong></span></span>警方接獲遺失裝備報告後立即展開調查，案件列作「遺失政府財物」，由有關人員所屬單位跟進調查。警方稱，該部平板電腦並沒有個人資料。<br />\n<br />\n警方重申，警隊就裝備的保管及使用有嚴格的規定，將會繼續跟進有關事件，呼籲市民如拾獲有關物品，應立即致電999或把物品交到就近的警署。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200105/s00001/1578238171353/o%e8%a8%98%e6%8e%a2%e5%93%a1%e6%97%ba%e8%a7%92%e5%9f%b7%e5%8b%a4%e9%81%ba%e5%a4%b1%e8%a3%9d%e5%82%99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200105%2Fs00001%2F1578238171353%2Fo%25e8%25a8%2598%25e6%258e%25a2%25e5%2593%25a1%25e6%2597%25ba%25e8%25a7%2592%25e5%259f%25b7%25e5%258b%25a4%25e9%2581%25ba%25e5%25a4%25b1%25e8%25a3%259d%25e5%2582%2599&d=4MF4O%2Bfy8eJNXT4C%2FvKi1T2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=2dbdf10c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200105%2Fs00001%2F1578238171353%2Fo%25e8%25a8%2598%25e6%258e%25a2%25e5%2593%25a1%25e6%2597%25ba%25e8%25a7%2592%25e5%259f%25b7%25e5%258b%25a4%25e9%2581%25ba%25e5%25a4%25b1%25e8%25a3%259d%25e5%2582%2599&h=06876e59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200105/s00001/1578238171353/o%e8%a8%98%e6%8e%a2%e5%93%a1%e6%97%ba%e8%a7%92%e5%9f%b7%e5%8b%a4%e9%81%ba%e5%a4%b1%e8%a3%9d%e5%82%99</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>電筒定係laser beam?</strong>"},{"pid":"3474fafdd0c978e6949c3a53ecc9ba0b6efc038b","tid":1812903,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"